#
# Description: test cases for histo.c

# First example
# Contains negative integers and different spacing (space, tab, newline)
echo -e "3 -4 5 1 7 0\n8 0 15 12 3 5\n3 3 3 3\n\t-5\t 3" | ./histo
16 bins of size 1 for range [0,16)
[ 0:0 ] **
[ 1:1 ] *
[ 2:2 ] 
[ 3:3 ] *******
